import rackets_list from "./rackets/rackets"
import shoes_list from "./shoes"
import grips from "./grips"
import bands from "./bands"
import strings from "./strings"
import dampeners from "./dampeners"
import bags from "./bags"

const products_data = {
    'rackets': rackets_list,
    'shoes': shoes_list,
    'grips': grips,
    'bands': bands,
    'strings': strings,
    'dampeners': dampeners,
    'bags': bags
}

export default products_data
